query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info in ('LD master format','LD release date','LD laserdisc title','death notes','LD frequency response','LD color information','LD disc size','portrayed in','sound mix','filming dates','locations','LD sound encoding','LD catalog number','pictorial','LD language','rating','LD color rendition','soundtrack','LD audio noise','birth notes','LD video artifacts') AND (k.keyword like '%secrets%' OR k.keyword like '%alien%') AND t.production_year > 2009 AND t.production_year < 2012 AND (t.title like '%shield%' OR t.title like '%thriller%' OR t.title like '%violin%' OR t.title like '%woman%') AND kt.kind in ('video game','movie') AND chn.name not like '%Wonder Woman%' AND chn.name not like '%Rocky Balboa%' AND chn.name not like '%The Terminator%' AND chn.name not like '%Joker%' AND chn.name not like '%Rocky Balboa%' AND cct2.kind in ('cast','complete','complete+verified') AND n.name not like '%x%' AND n.name not like '%u%' AND n.name not like '%S%' AND n.name not like '%b%' AND n.gender in ('m') AND mi_idx.info > '10.0'
